### 🧑‍🎓 Register Student
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/students/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "roll": "22071A0500",
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 🧑‍🎓 Upload Student Photo (replace {student_id} with real ID returned above)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/students/22071A0500/upload_photo
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="alice1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/alice1.jpg
--boundary--

